text: Bình Hòa is a ward of Thuận An town in Bình Dương Province of Southeast region of Vietnam. First Vietnam Singapore Industrial Park (VSIP) is located in Bình Đáng near An Phú ward. ==Administrative divisions== Bình Hòa is divided into 8 neighborhoods: * Bình Đức 1 * Bình Đức 2 * Bình Đức 3 * Bình Đáng * Đồng An 1 * Đồng An 2 * Đồng An 3 * Đông Ba ==References== Category:Populated places in Bình Dương Province
title: Bình Hòa, Bình Dương
